item.description:
@Uncalled wrote:

The difference between PI and Delta is that Delta is sloppy coding and very laggy. PI sources are very nicely set-up and more stable then Delta. Delta is easier to code, yes but, it’s so laggy and horribly coded. Things are just scattered everywhere instead of everything being at its own thing. If you’d really like to see the difference, just download a PI source and a Delta and just go through the files of each one.

item.description:
